OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773774690
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,FA registered sex offender has been
OL,7,Fjailed after being caught by Live
OL,8,FFacial Recognition technology.
OL,10,FOfficers were alerted and vans were
OL,11,Fdeployed after cameras flagged Phillip
OL,12,FLoxam, 57, from Stockport, in the town
OL,13,Fcentre on 12 February 2026.
OL,15,FHe was questioned for a number of
OL,16,Foffences, including having software on
OL,17,Fhis phone to conceal its internet
OL,18,Fhistory.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
