CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773774690
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,FLoxam was also found to have a
OL,7,Fconcealed second unregistered mobile
OL,8,Fphone, which was found on him after
OL,9,Fhis arrest.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police said around
OL,12,F20% of arrests made using the
OL,13,Ftechnology since it was introduced
OL,14,Fhave involved registered sex
OL,15,Foffenders, and about three-quarters of
OL,16,Fsuspects identified through the system
OL,17,Fhave gone on to be charged with
OL,18,Foffences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
