CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773774690
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,FLoxam appeared at Minshull Street
OL,7,FCrown Court on Friday 13 March when he
OL,8,Fadmitted three breaches of his Sexual
OL,9,FHarm Prevention Order (SHPO). He was
OL,10,Fjailed then for 20 months.
OL,12,FHe was previously handed a 20 month
OL,13,Fprison sentence in July 2024 for seven
OL,14,Fbreaches of his SHPO.
OL,16,FEarlier this month, John Thompson, 43,
OL,17,Ffrom Manchester, was jailed for 16
OL,18,Fmonths after admitting to a total of
OL,19,F35 breaches of his SHPO and a breach
OL,20,Fof his sex offender notification
OL,21,Frequirements.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
