OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773774690
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,FThompson had also been on Greater
OL,7,FManchester Police's (GMP) watchlist
OL,8,Fand was spotted by one of the LFR
OL,9,Fcameras in Piccadilly Gardens on 28
OL,10,FJanuary.
OL,12,FThere has been a total of 53 arrests
OL,13,Fsince we started deploying LFR in
OL,14,FOctober 2025, 11 of which have been
OL,15,FRSOs.
OL,17,FThe vans have been supplied by the
OL,18,FHome Office and will be used by forces
OL,19,Facross the north west.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
